---
- Document public interfaces with clear docstrings
- Use README.md for high-level documentation and user guides
- Include examples in documentation where applicable
- Update CHANGELOG.md for all significant changes
- Maintain proper versioning across all version references (pyproject.toml, __init__.py, etc.)
- For complex functionality, include comments explaining the reasoning
